  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To assess the efficacy and safety of oral rosuvastatin in patients with suspected or
      confirmed influenza who require intensive care unit (ICU) admission due to respiratory
      distress.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Hypothesis: Rosuvastatin therapy will improve mortality and reduce the need for mechanical
      ventilation in patients experiencing respiratory distress as a complication of influenza.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
